name: Celaray
description: Riding the wind, this Pal travels where it pleases. Should it find a partner along the way, the encounter will mark its journey's end.

partner_skill.name: Zephyr Glider
partner_skill.description: While in team, can be summoned and used instead of a glider.Allows you to move quickly for long periods of time while gliding with this Pal.

active_skills.name: Hydro Jet
active_skills.description:
Hurls a high speed ball of water
at an enemy.

active_skills.name: Aqua Gun
active_skills.description:
Hurls a ball of water
straight at an enemy.

active_skills.name: Power Shot
active_skills.description:
Charges energy
into a focused blast.

active_skills.name: Bubble Blast
active_skills.description:
Fires numerous bubbles
that slowly pursue an enemy.

active_skills.name: Seed Machine Gun
active_skills.description:
Fires a volley of hard seeds
at enemies in front of it.

active_skills.name: Aqua Burst
active_skills.description:
Creates a giant ball of water
and hurls it at an enemy.

active_skills.name: Hydro Laser
active_skills.description:
Shoots pressurized water at extreme velocities,
sweeping over a wide area in front of it.
